Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:04.700
Signifiers, are communication devices. That tell people

00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:07.610
what to do, and where to do it.

00:00:07.610 --> 00:00:10.690
Think about it. People oftentimes, need some way

00:00:10.690 --> 00:00:12.780
of understanding a product or service they wish

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:18.670
to use. Some sign of what it is for. What is happening, and what the alternative

00:00:18.670 --> 00:00:23.210
actions are. People search for clues, for any

00:00:23.210 --> 00:00:26.070
sign that might help them cope and understand.

00:00:26.070 --> 00:00:29.710
And these signs, are called signifiers.

